{
  "page": "House Wydman",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Wydman</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Wydman.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Wydman.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Wydman.svg/250px-House_Wydman.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Wydman.svg/375px-House_Wydman.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/House_Wydman.svg/500px-House_Wydman.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"width:100%;min-width:300px;position:relative;z-index:100;border:0 grey solid;margin-top:-3em;margin-bottom:1em;\"><div style=\"display: table; width: calc(100% - 80px); height: 28px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px; margin: 0px auto 0px; padding: 0;border:0; position: relative; border-collapse:collapse; text-align: center; font-family: &#39;Uncial Antiqua&#39;; color: #00f; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ddd 0%, #ddd 10%, #dd0 10%, #dd0 90%, #ddd 90%);\">\n  <div style=\"display:table-cell; vertical-align: middle; padding: 4px; clip-path: polygon(2px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 2px calc(100% - 2px)); background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fff 0%, #fff 10%, #ff0 10%, #ff0 90%, #fff 90%);\">Right Conquers Might</div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 5px calc(100% - 2px), calc(25% + 3px) 50%, 5px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, 75% 50%, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 2px) 5px, calc(75% + 3px) 50%); background: #fff;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%, 25% 50%); background: #ddd;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(2px calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 5px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(75% - 3px) 50%, calc(100% - 5px) 2px, 2px 2px, 25% 50%, 2px calc(100% - 2px), 2px 5px, calc(25% - 3px) 50%); background: #fff;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 75% 50%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); background: #ddd;\"></div></div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\n5 splintered lances, 3-2, striped blue and white with blue pennons, on yellow, beneath a white chief bearing a red castle, a green viper, a black broken wheel, a purple unicorn and a golden lion<br />(<i>Yellow, five broken lances, 3-2, striped azure and argent, pennons of the second, on a chief of the third, a wheel broken sable between, on the dexter, a castle gules and snake vert, and, on the sinister, a unicorn purpure and lion or</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founder</th><td>\nA <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Citadel_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Citadel-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Wydman</b> is a noble house from the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a>. It blazons its arms with 5 splintered lances, 3-2, striped blue and white with blue pennons, on yellow, beneath a white chief bearing a red castle, a green <a href=\"/index.php/Snake\" title=\"Snake\">viper</a>, a black broken wheel, a purple <a href=\"/index.php/Unicorn\" title=\"Unicorn\">unicorn</a> and a golden <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-heraldry_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-heraldry-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Its words are \"Right Conquers Might.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#House_Wydman_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Wydman at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wydman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The coat of arms of House Wydman derives from a <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> in which the founder of the house bested five <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> from the Vale and <a href=\"/index.php/The_Westerlands\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Westerlands\">the Westerlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Citadel_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Citadel-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The arms of the defeated, which are displayed above the five broken lances of the Wydmans, suggest Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Redfort\" title=\"House Redfort\">Redfort</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lynderly\" title=\"House Lynderly\">Lynderly</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Waynwood\" title=\"House Waynwood\">Waynwood</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Brax\" title=\"House Brax\">Brax</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wydman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wydman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>A noble displaying a broken lance is present in the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie#High_Hall_of_the_Arryns\" title=\"Eyrie\">High Hall</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a> when <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> demands a <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_by_battle\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Trial by battle\">trial by battle</a> to prove his innocence of the claims put against him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Wydman_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Wydman at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wydman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Wydman at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Wydmans during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>no member has appeared yet.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wydman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Citadel-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Citadel_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Citadel_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. Heraldry: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Entry/House_Wydman/\">House Wydman</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-heraldry-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-heraldry_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. Heraldry: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/5/\">Houses in the Vale</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Mottoes/\">House Mottoes</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, Tyrion V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:HousesVale\" title=\"Template:HousesVale\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:HousesVale&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:HousesVale (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:HousesVale&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;bor